==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: chéng yĕ xiāohé, bài yĕ xiāohé
===Etymology===
In the beginning of the Han Dynasty, [[w:Xiao He|Xiao He]] recommended [[w:Han Xin|Han Xin]] become a general, later he helped [[w:Empress Lü Zhi|Empress Lü Zhi]] to have him killed.  Later, this phrase was used as a metaphor to describe a situation in the success or failure of an endeavor derives from the same person or thing.

===Idiom===
'''[[成]][[也]][[蕭何]]，[[敗]][[也]][[蕭何]]'''
# the reason for his success is also his undoing
# the reason for their success is also their undoing
#: '''''成也萧何败也萧何''' [[低]][[成本]][[成]][[沃尔玛]][[命门]]''
#: '''''成也蕭何敗也蕭何''' [[低]][[成本]][[成]][[沃爾瑪]][[命門]]''
#: '''''The reason for their success was also their undoing''', low cost was the mandate of Walmart''
# not dependable; now yes, now no; always changing

